			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Crude steel is a key material in global production, with its demand and production increasing, particularly in China. In 2011, worldwide production reached over 1.5 billion tons. By 2021, this figure had risen to just under two billion metric tons, a 4% increase from 2020. However, production rates from electric arc furnaces have decreased. Clean steel, a type of steel with low levels of impurities, oxides, inclusions, or carbon, is also significant in the steel sector.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">粗钢是全球生产的关键材料，其需求和产量都在不断增长，尤其是在中国。2011 年，全球产量超过 15 亿吨。到 2021 年，这一数字上升到略低于 20 亿吨，比 2020 年增长了 4%。然而，电弧炉的生产率却有所下降。洁净钢是一种杂质、氧化物、夹杂物或碳含量较低的钢材，在钢铁行业也占有重要地位。</common:generalComment>
